This is a list of properties and historic districts in [Iowa](/Iowa) that are listed on the [National Register of Historic Places](/National_Register_of_Historic_Places). The state boasts an impressive number of listings, with properties found in all of [Iowa's 99 counties](/List_of_Iowa_counties), accumulating to a total exceeding 2,300 entries. It's a testament to the state's rich and varied past, a tapestry woven from the lives and endeavors of those who came before.

### Contents: Counties in Iowa

The following is a comprehensive, albeit sometimes tedious, compilation of Iowa's counties, each with its own unique narrative etched into the landscape. Clicking on a county name will lead you to a more detailed exploration of its historical treasures. *Italicized entries denote links to separate pages for more in-depth information.*

